sequenceDiagram
    participant Source as Source Wallet
    participant Keeper as Keeper (Lambda/Bot)
    participant RPC as RPC / Blockchain
    participant Safe as Safe Wallet

    Source->>Keeper: approve(keeper, amount)
    loop Monitor Balance
        Keeper->>RPC: check balanceOf(Source) or listen Transfer events
        alt balance >= threshold
            Keeper->>RPC: send transferFrom(Source, Safe, balance)
            RPC->>Safe: USDC received
        end
    end
